WEBVTT

00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:04.956
Well, good morning, family, good evening wherever you are.

00:00:04.957 --> 00:00:16.399
I talk to people all over the world, so I always say morning. Thank you for joining us again tonight. We have some work to do.

00:00:16.400 --> 00:00:26.999
I don't even really know where to start other than I just want to give God all the praise and glory for what he's doing. As we see, prayer changes things.

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:43.192
We see Pam Bondi and the man saying that he wanted to harm her, trying to pay $45,000, which was around—I saw 50 on the wanted.

00:00:43.193 --> 00:00:50.760
As I have been praying over this today, I have more to share with you.

00:00:50.761 --> 00:00:55.584
The Lord is revealing more to us, Diana and I, and my children.

00:00:55.585 --> 00:01:19.097
As we were driving around, I saw a football, and Pam Bondi was holding a football, but I didn't understand what I was seeing on the 19th.

00:01:19.098 --> 00:01:40.283
When I saw her holding the football, I said, 'This looks like a football, but it has layers.'It transformed from a football to a pinwheel that had layers that looked dark black and white.

00:01:40.284 --> 00:01:44.262
That's why I said it looked like one of those Hostess cupcakes.

00:01:44.263 --> 00:01:53.758
It had the frosting all in it, and it was pinwheel-looking, and the football turned into that.

00:01:53.759 --> 00:02:06.099
The Lord said there are many layers to this for her to expose.

00:02:06.100 --> 00:02:19.518
She's going to expose this darkness, but she needs a little bit more information to nail the coffin closed and make it a closed case.

00:02:19.519 --> 00:02:32.597
She has enough evidence that she's going to run with this. The Lord said because of what she will expose, there will be a price on her head.

00:02:32.598 --> 00:02:46.677
I saw a price tag of over $50,000. I saw the zeros, and I saw not 45, but 50.

00:02:46.678 --> 00:02:59.951
As I saw this red list, I saw Alex Jones was going to expose some things that were dark, and what he would say would be credible.

00:02:59.952 --> 00:03:12.745
I saw Tucker Carlson on the list. I saw many judges on this hit list and people in high authority—Giuliani.

00:03:12.746 --> 00:03:22.568
I saw many people on this list, and some of their names had more zeros than others.

00:03:22.569 --> 00:03:55.919
The Lord said, 'You must pray for their protection, for they are on a list to be taken out, and you must intercede for them, for this is bigger than you realize.'I saw foreign people—and I can't go into all that—who were funding this through crypto.

00:03:55.920 --> 00:04:27.856
That's all I'm going to say. We're going to continue to pray for them because the Lord said what was said today was communication.

00:04:27.857 --> 00:04:45.519
It's bigger than the man that was caught today; this is communication. Why would they have this gambling ring?

00:04:45.520 --> 00:04:57.184
And why would some of these people who are worth millions participate in this? They're already worth millions of dollars.

00:04:57.185 --> 00:05:15.528
Why would they risk their chance of going to prison for a couple million dollars for these big people?

00:05:15.529 --> 00:05:23.356
You are thinking too small. That's what the Lord said. Blackmail. Blackmail tapes, videotapes.

00:05:23.357 --> 00:05:40.471
The Lord said videotapes with them doing certain things with certain young people. Blackmail.

00:05:40.472 --> 00:05:53.062
'Do what we tell you to do or more will come out.'This is deeper than what you can ever understand.

00:05:53.063 --> 00:06:02.533
And the Lord said—and that's all I will say about that—but you must know that it doesn't make sense.

00:06:02.534 --> 00:06:15.703
You can play the video of what the Lord said. Yes, sir. Go ahead, son.

00:06:15.704 --> 00:06:28.441
Just play it right there and show them what the Lord said. Football, baseball...

00:06:28.442 --> 00:06:32.899
oh, and sports people. And then he talked to us about LeBron James, and I thought that was interesting.

00:06:32.900 --> 00:06:44.478
He said he'll retire soon. Everybody says, 'Well, of course he will.'No, I'm talking about something more to this.

00:06:44.479 --> 00:07:04.319
I saw the king be dethroned—the name King James. There's more to this, and it was not a good thing.

00:07:04.320 --> 00:07:25.439
The Lord said he would be dethroned. A humbling is coming. I don't know what that means, but I saw a humbling coming, a play on words. I'm just telling you what I saw.

00:07:25.440 --> 00:07:38.243
There's something more to a dethroning of a king who considers himself way above the King of Kings, the Lord of Lords, Jesus Christ.

00:07:38.244 --> 00:07:51.792
King James Version, King—all this stuff was in the air. But the Lord said, 'There's about to be something huge happen in the NBA.

00:07:51.793 --> 00:08:07.599
There's about to be something huge happen in the NFL and the major league.'He said, 'Watch what I'm about to do in these areas.'So, that's what we were praying over.

00:08:07.600 --> 00:08:16.233
You see, it's bigger than you realize. The Lord said this several weeks ago.

00:08:16.234 --> 00:08:31.282
He said, 'Pray for an exposing of dark things: NFL, Major League Baseball, and the NBA.'It will be in all these arenas.

00:08:31.283 --> 00:08:36.811
I saw major corruption. The Lord said it will be an uncovering.

00:08:36.812 --> 00:08:42.371
And that's what this pinwheel is. And I'm telling you, she had a football.

00:08:42.372 --> 00:08:48.079
I said, 'What is this?'because we're not even talking about football; we're talking about basketball and some of this stuff.

00:08:48.080 --> 00:09:38.319
But the Lord said there's deep dark corruption. And if you go back to what I saw concerning the children, consider the children trafficking.

00:09:38.320 --> 00:09:53.100
It's much deeper than most of you will ever realize. But as this happens, if we pray into this, the Lord said he has a hand on it.

00:09:53.101 --> 00:10:00.079
I'm telling you, we will see revival break out in major sporting events.

00:10:00.080 --> 00:10:15.463
I saw major key players having a major revival and the Holy Ghost taking over the NFL, NBA, and Major League Baseball.

00:10:15.464 --> 00:10:29.195
We're going to see people that are going to get really radical for Jesus in the days ahead, a major revival they will be used to bring forth.

00:10:29.196 --> 00:10:42.212
The Lord is going to pour out his spirit on our sports. People will idolize them like gods, like Michael Jordans and all the celebrities.

00:10:42.213 --> 00:10:48.078
The Lord said he's going to use that celebrity for his glory for bringing in the harvest.

00:10:48.079 --> 00:11:07.754
Watch what he does with these young people. But even more so with the music industry—the Lord said pray over the music industry. Pray over all this for there's an uncovering.

00:11:07.755 --> 00:11:25.679
Even when I told you I saw a new Democratic woman being groomed by the devil, hand-selected by the devil, I saw this woman being raised up and appointed.

00:11:25.680 --> 00:11:34.022
Even when I told you yesterday I saw this new pastor coming to Australia—I keep seeing these key figures.

00:11:34.023 --> 00:11:43.613
The Lord's hand-selecting people, and the devil's trying to hand-select people. It's interesting to me because I keep seeing both sides.

00:11:43.614 --> 00:11:56.256
The Lord's showing me the devil picking people to try to cause great distraction and disruption in the move. And then you see God saying, 'I'm raising up these people.

00:11:56.257 --> 00:12:03.180
I'm going to raise up new men with great voices like David's, Hannah's, and Esther's, and they're going to be prayer people.

00:12:03.181 --> 00:12:09.858
They're going to be the closers.'The Lord keeps talking about all this, but then I keep seeing the enemy and he has his plan.

00:12:09.859 --> 00:12:17.537
But we know who has the greater plan. Greater is he that is in us than he that is in the world.

00:12:17.538 --> 00:12:45.350
The Lord told us, 'You're about to see weather manipulation, weaponized weather more than what you've ever seen before.'He said that even last night with ice storms, winter cyclones, heavy snowfall, blizzard conditions in Buffalo, and lake effect snow that will be the largest we've ever seen.

00:12:45.351 --> 00:12:50.622
I'm talking about seeing major weather events in the days ahead.

00:12:50.623 --> 00:13:00.102
Well, you say, 'Well, Brandon, we have weather events all the time.'Yes, but this is going to be different from what I saw.

00:13:00.103 --> 00:13:11.250
I saw major winds, major straight-line winds, and power outages that would go for a thousand miles.

00:13:11.251 --> 00:13:20.239
I'm talking about crippling ice storms. The Lord said, 'You have to pray over the weather.'That's why I brought all that up last night.

00:13:20.240 --> 00:13:33.557
I was trying to encourage you to use your authority over drought and rain. As he is, so are we in this world.

00:13:33.558 --> 00:13:44.398
The Lord was showing us: 'Brandon, if I can call peace to the storms, I've given you the ability to pray over it also.'As he is, so are we in this world.

00:13:44.399 --> 00:13:55.119
I just wanted to encourage you all when I showed you how much rain northern Oklahoma got, all over Tulsa.

00:13:55.120 --> 00:14:12.100
Every time I call in a certain number, I say I'm waiting for over five inches of rain to come over our land, fill our rivers, our ponds, our creeks, and our lakes so that we don't have a drought.

00:14:12.101 --> 00:14:16.817
We take authority over drought. We call the rain in Jesus'name.

00:14:16.818 --> 00:14:38.353
You have authority to do that. Pray over your weather. There it is, right there.

00:14:38.354 --> 00:14:49.877
Everywhere in Tulsa, the rain came. That's what the Lord was trying to show you. You can do that to your town. You can call in the rain.

00:14:49.878 --> 00:14:59.070
That's why I was praying over Australia, because I saw a great drought and that even the kangaroos would die because there's no water.

00:14:59.071 --> 00:15:10.820
I saw the lakes and the ponds completely dry with big cracks, and the land was like tumbleweeds blowing across.

00:15:10.821 --> 00:15:22.354
It was so bad. The Lord said, 'Pray for the rain. Pray for the rain.'That's what I was trying to show you.

00:15:22.355 --> 00:15:26.631
We started calling it in because we hadn't had rain in September, October, or November.

00:15:26.632 --> 00:15:33.009
Hey sweetie, you want to come sit by me? I'll get out and then you can come sit down.

00:15:33.010 --> 00:15:39.716
I have my buddy. Sorry, I didn't want to disturb you. You're good.

00:15:39.717 --> 00:15:56.447
Come sit down by me. You look so marvelous. So, we're just talking about all the rain and everything.

00:15:56.448 --> 00:16:01.670
We were praying over the rain, believing God for supernatural rain.

00:16:01.671 --> 00:16:06.335
If you ever read anything, you hold it out of your mouth, don't you?

00:16:06.336 --> 00:16:11.172
Well, you can read about the blood. I have the book. We read that book last night.

00:16:11.173 --> 00:16:15.652
When you started reading, I felt the presence of the Lord. Did you?

00:16:15.653 --> 00:16:23.504
I don't know if they did, but I did. That's all that matters. But I'm reading about the precious blood of Jesus.

00:16:23.505 --> 00:16:36.425
You know, these little pocketbooks you can get for a buck. I love reading stuff like that, filling yourself up and being controlled by the Holy Ghost.

00:16:36.426 --> 00:16:59.101
We were listening to Corrie ten Boom today, and it was wonderful. It was on YouTube and it blessed me.

00:16:59.102 --> 00:17:15.734
It made me really go deep inside of myself to say, 'Listen, you've got to come up higher.'Beautiful. She challenged me, this lady did.

00:17:15.735 --> 00:17:24.879
We didn't even finish it, but I just want to encourage everyone to find things that will inspire you.

00:17:24.880 --> 00:17:30.355
Find things that will fan your flame to keep that fire going.

00:17:30.356 --> 00:17:36.875
Don't wait on your pastor or whoever is over you that you listen to.

00:17:36.876 --> 00:17:41.412
Don't wait on them to feed you Wednesdays and Sundays or whenever you go to church.

00:17:41.413 --> 00:17:47.715
You've got to have that bulldog-on-a-bone faith to say, 'Hey, I'm going to feed myself.

00:17:47.716 --> 00:17:54.222
I've got to get out there and get a hold of something. I cannot wait for somebody to spoon-feed me.

00:17:54.223 --> 00:18:05.298
I've got to have enough to be a scavenger. I'm going to find something and live by faith, and I don't need somebody else to feed me.

00:18:05.299 --> 00:18:08.760
I'm going to feed myself.'That's what Diana and I have always done.

00:18:08.761 --> 00:18:19.152
When Megan was first diagnosed with autism, we couldn't really go to church because it was such a distraction.

00:18:19.153 --> 00:18:24.880
For all those years, we just learned how to feed ourselves. We fought.

00:18:24.881 --> 00:18:33.351
I said we're going to keep going with this and we're going to find the word for whatever we need.

00:18:33.352 --> 00:18:45.759
A lot of times, it was always Kenneth E. Hagin. I listen to Brother Hagin most of all, and then to the people we listen to now.

00:18:45.760 --> 00:18:52.954
Just keep fanning that flame. Listen to Lynn Hammond. Stir up how to pray in the spirit.

00:18:52.955 --> 00:19:02.736
How bad do you want change in your life? How hungry and desperate are you for change?

00:19:02.737 --> 00:19:07.936
Are you willing to go out and look for something versus sitting there waiting?

00:19:07.937 --> 00:19:15.115
I'm telling you, it comes to the point where I see a lot of these people say, 'Brandon, I need all this.'Get it.

00:19:15.116 --> 00:19:19.808
Be a contender. Fight for it. Nobody's going to just give it to you.

00:19:19.809 --> 00:19:26.957
You have to want it bad enough. I want change. I want the Holy Ghost in my life. I want the glory and the presence.

00:19:26.958 --> 00:19:46.442
I want Jesus manifested in my home so that whenever I have an issue, when you're overcoming something, when you get a bad report, or when you have a bill you can't pay and the creditors are calling, you know what to do.

00:19:46.443 --> 00:19:55.708
If you have a need, you sow a seed. That's what we learned. He said he gives you wisdom to get wealth.

00:19:55.709 --> 00:20:03.971
So, we believe God and he gives us wisdom to make money. But what happens if you need a doctor's report?

00:20:03.972 --> 00:20:09.901
You find scripture. That's what we always do. We go back to the word.

00:20:09.902 --> 00:20:16.853
Find scriptures that pertain to what you're believing for and quote those scriptures over your life.

00:20:16.854 --> 00:20:24.298
We have Bibles everywhere. Diana got a waterproof Bible. I thought that was perfect for the end times.

00:20:24.299 --> 00:20:35.501
You could hide it in the woods. The Antichrist is going to take everybody's Bible away. I don't even think that would burn.

00:20:35.502 --> 00:20:43.999
I just know we're in a time like we've never seen before, and it's going to keep increasing.

00:20:44.000 --> 00:20:53.323
As of the 23rd, I know there is an acceleration, and we're about to see things we've never seen before.

00:20:53.324 --> 00:21:01.308
I have an urgency to come on here all the time to pray and to tell you all that Jesus Christ is coming and you've got to get your house in order.

00:21:01.309 --> 00:21:06.074
People ask, 'What does that mean, Brandon?'Well, what does that feel like to you?

00:21:06.075 --> 00:21:15.918
What is the Lord telling you to do? Do you have an urgency in your spirit to draw close to him?

00:21:15.919 --> 00:21:28.239
Does he know you? If you were to have a face-to-face encounter with the Lord, would he say, 'I know them'?

00:21:28.240 --> 00:21:37.678
Or would he say, "You know, you may know a lot about the Father, but does he know you?

00:21:37.679 --> 00:21:53.832
Do you just go and visit once a month or once a year at church, or do you have a relationship every single day with him?"If I only had a relationship with Diana every month or every year, there wouldn't be a good marriage.

00:21:53.833 --> 00:21:57.698
A marriage is based on having a relationship every single day.

00:21:57.699 --> 00:22:02.399
We talk, we have communion. That's what I'm trying to tell you. That's the way it is with the Father.

00:22:02.400 --> 00:22:10.865
You must have a relationship with him and find things that will inspire you to keep going: books, tape series, whatever.

00:22:10.866 --> 00:22:15.025
Back in the day, I used to buy a tape series every single time I got paid.

00:22:15.026 --> 00:22:20.845
I'd find a tape series and I'd listen to that one tape series the whole time because we only got paid every two weeks.

00:22:20.846 --> 00:22:38.957
I said if I could listen to it every time, whether it would be usually Lester Sumrall or somebody like that, I'd find something and think, "Man, I want to listen to these old-timers."I would listen to that whole tape series for two weeks and then I'd alternate them out just continually.

00:22:38.957 --> 00:22:50.418
Faith cometh by hearing, and hearing by the word of God. The only way you're going to get strong is with your faith growing. But faith works by love, so you've got to keep strife out.

00:22:50.419 --> 00:23:01.776
I'm telling you, it's like seeing an engine where the pistons and all the parts are moving in the engine so that you go really fast.

00:23:01.777 --> 00:23:07.688
But if one thing is off, that engine is not going to work right. That's the way it is in the spirit realm.

00:23:07.689 --> 00:23:17.763
You've got to make sure all those pistons are firing and all that stuff in the spirit is firing and going perfectly so that you're going forward in your spiritual walk.

00:23:17.764 --> 00:23:28.274
That's going to make that spiritual car go forward. If not, you're going to be idle and sitting by, asking, "Why am I still this way after all these years?

00:23:28.275 --> 00:23:39.446
How come nothing's changed?"Most people keep doing the same thing expecting different results, and that's the definition of insanity.

00:23:39.447 --> 00:23:50.399
That's why I say if it isn't working after 30 days, or if it isn't working after 60 days, we've got to make some changes in here.

00:23:50.400 --> 00:24:01.898
If what you're doing isn't getting you closer to God after a couple of weeks and you're saying, "Well, I'm still idly sitting by,"the Bible says if we draw nigh to him, he'll draw nigh to us.

00:24:01.899 --> 00:24:13.754
So I'm just looking, "Father, I want more. I'm desperate, I'm hungry, I'm thirsty."For you said those that hunger and thirst after righteousness shall be filled.

00:24:13.755 --> 00:24:19.478
I believe with all my heart that my wife and I are hungry, thirsty, and desperate.

00:24:19.479 --> 00:24:27.839
For the eyes of the Lord are running to and fro throughout the whole earth, looking for a heart who's perfect towards him.

00:24:27.840 --> 00:24:39.689
If the eyes of the Lord are running to and fro throughout the whole earth, looking for a heart who's perfect towards him, let his eyes rest on me. Help me, O Lord, to have a perfect heart.

00:24:39.690 --> 00:24:53.359
Create in me a clean heart, Lord, so that you can look at me and say, "Hey, I want to go and visit his house."I make him feel comfortable in my home.

00:24:53.360 --> 00:25:00.395
I create an atmosphere of worship in the house. I usually have worship playing all the time on the TV.

00:25:00.396 --> 00:25:12.677
I said, "Man, if Jesus showed up right now, would he be happy to be here?"Or would he go, "You know what?

00:25:12.678 --> 00:25:21.472
I look at the time, I need to keep walking down the road here."Or would he go, "Hey, you know what?

00:25:21.473 --> 00:25:36.079
I'd like to take my sandals off here and sit down and visit. Can we just have a little bit of tea? Let's have that iced tea, son. I'd like to sit down and talk.

00:25:36.080 --> 00:25:49.365
Just have a little talk with Jesus."So, I just try to inspire you all to get close to him before we get into the real serious stuff with Pam Bondi and all the things that the Lord has shown us.

00:25:49.366 --> 00:25:59.835
It all comes out of relationship. I'm going to be real with y'all: I have issues, Diana has issues, Braden has—we all have issues.

00:25:59.836 --> 00:26:09.702
But we diligently seek him. We want him more than we want air. I want him more than I want water.

00:26:09.703 --> 00:26:14.330
I'm a big guy and I'm overweight, and I want him more than I want food.

00:26:14.331 --> 00:26:38.205
How much more do you want the Father in your life and change? I don't want to live tomorrow the same way I did today. I don't want to be this way this time next year.

00:26:38.206 --> 00:26:48.179
Smith Wigglesworth said, "If you don't see change in your life spiritually every three days, you're backsliding."That challenged me.

00:26:48.180 --> 00:26:56.176
I thought, "Backsliding? Wow."Because we're supposed to be going from glory to glory.

00:26:56.177 --> 00:27:15.038
He's changing us into his likeness and image to perfect in me the love of God shown to the world.

00:27:15.039 --> 00:27:21.831
I know there's more, even with all the things that the Lord has graciously shown me.

00:27:21.832 --> 00:27:29.359
For whatever reason he chooses to show me anything, I know there's more.

00:27:29.360 --> 00:27:42.189
When you see beyond the veil, you know there's much more. If I could just camp there.

00:27:42.190 --> 00:27:49.602
There are rooms in the spirit, places in the spirit where you can go.

00:27:49.603 --> 00:28:05.759
I can go to certain rooms in the spirit, and you know when you visit there that the room is vast, but there are levels of glory and levels of relationship.

00:28:05.760 --> 00:28:16.239
So many people are like the chickens pecking around, but you were created for so much more.

00:28:16.240 --> 00:28:24.173
He made you to be an eagle to soar, and you can go anywhere you want while praying in the spirit.

00:28:24.174 --> 00:28:30.988
But if you choose to be a chicken, you only stay in that barnyard.

00:28:30.989 --> 00:28:43.038
God's called you to come up higher, like the eagles, and soar with him in the high places. There's so much more.

00:28:43.039 --> 00:28:55.760
When I was my son's age, I would fast and pray every other day because I just wanted to see the dead raised.

00:28:55.761 --> 00:29:02.967
I still do. I wanted to see the blinded eyes open. I want to hear the Father.

00:29:02.968 --> 00:29:09.599
I want to have a relationship with him. I don't like religion.

00:29:09.600 --> 00:29:21.557
And I know that there's a place in God where you experience that glory that Satan dare not go. He's scared spitless when you come up in there.

00:29:21.558 --> 00:29:36.963
Even when we can see when people have demonic spirits and we've got the glory and we feel it—we feel that 'oozing'as I call it, that overflow coming out of you—they start to manifest when they get around you.

00:29:36.964 --> 00:29:49.839
I'm telling you, the devil is scared spitless of the anointing and the presence of God and a Christian that understands and knows who they are.

00:29:49.840 --> 00:29:56.639
He's scared spitless of them, but he's not scared of the ones that don't know who they are.

00:29:56.640 --> 00:30:14.798
I said, "You can quote Bible, you can quote books, and it would be like saying, 'Twinkle, Twinkle, Little Star'if you don't realize who you are."He knows the difference between one who knows it and one who doesn't.

00:30:14.799 --> 00:30:26.690
There is a level of authority that the devil is scared of. It's like having a police officer dressed in uniform.

00:30:26.691 --> 00:30:39.278
It's the authority of the government that backs him when he says, "Stop."His outfit doesn't really make anyone stop; it's what the outfit represents.

00:30:39.279 --> 00:30:46.879
The moment he puts his hand up like that, that's all he has to do to a big old semitruck.

00:30:46.880 --> 00:30:57.740
Stop. And that semi will stop. Why? Because of what is backing that badge. What's backing him?

00:30:57.741 --> 00:31:09.546
Not just a gun on his hip or handcuffs, but the law of the land, the government, and what we set in motion as the United States of America backs him.

00:31:09.547 --> 00:31:20.207
And he knows all he has to do is just put his hand up. As a believer, everything that the Lord has given you, he is backing you.

00:31:20.208 --> 00:31:25.311
And you put that hand up. You say, "No, devil. You ain't robbing me of my stuff.

00:31:25.312 --> 00:31:28.574
You're not going to take my children. You're not going to take my marriage.

00:31:28.575 --> 00:31:33.918
You're not going to take my finances. No, devil."Why? Why does he have to back you?

00:31:33.919 --> 00:31:43.599
Because he knows when you know. He knows when you know who you are because you have that badge on.

